<HEADLINE>
<P>
UPDATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Daniel Cerone 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KCBS-TV anchor Bree Walker will be back as host for the fifth edition of 
"People Magazine on TV" when it comes along Aug. 16 on CBS. Walker also will do 
some on-location interviews for the hourlong program. 
</P>
<P>
The new season of PBS' "Great Performances" will be launched in October with 
Jerome Kern's classic musical, "Show Boat." The production, taped live at the 
Paper Mill Playhouse in New Jersey, features Eddie Bracken. 
</P>
<P>
In cable super-station TBS' August premiere of "Coming Home: A Rockin' 
Reunion," Dick Clark will feature a 1985 jam session with rock 'n' roll 
pioneers Jerry Lee Lewis, Carl Perkins, Johnny Cash and the late Ray Orbison. 
</P>
