OUTTAKES: BLOODY PG-13 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Pat H. Broeske 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Meanwhile, "Licence to Kill" is out as a graphic novel. But don't look for 
Timothy Dalton as a new comic book character. 
</P>
<P>
The English star -- known before Bond for more dignified roles -- has refused 
to allow his likeness to be licensed in the just-out book from Eclipse Comics. 
</P>
<P>
The rest of the film's cast, however, made it to the funny pages. Pat H. 
Broeske 
</P>
</TEXT>
