<P>
Costa Rica has barred former White House aide Oliver L. North and former U.S. 
National Security Adviser John M. Poindexter from entering its territory after 
a yearlong parliamentary probe into arms and drugs smuggling, Information 
Minister Jorge Urbina said in San Jose, the nation's capital. Also banned from 
