<SUBJECT>
<P>
POLICE ASSAULTS -- MASSACHUSETTS; DEMONSTRATIONS -- MASSACHUSETTS; VIOLENCE; 
CONTINENTAL AIRLINES; DISORDERLY CONDUCT; AIRLINE PASSENGERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072389-0081 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 85721 </DOCID>
<DATE>
