Airport in 1928, receives Historical Achievement Award from Robert Hayes at air 
show. ; Photo, B-1B bomber, one of 50 aircraft on display, drew many onlookers 
at Aviation Expo '89 air show at Van Nuys Airport on Saturday. ; Photo, Vintage 
World War II planes fly over Van Nuys Airport during Aviation Expo '89 air 
show, which attracted 50,000 people Saturday. JOAN M. ZOPH-PAHOYO / Los Angeles 
