<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072389-0132 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 85844 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 23, 1989, Sunday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 3; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
694 words 
</P>
