<P>
Column; Recording Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072389-0155 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 85903 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 23, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
